Dzhokhar Tsarnaev was convicted last week of planting two bombs at the finish line of the Boston Marathon in 2013 . 
  Judge George O'Toole told jurors on Tuesday they are not to attend this year's race or related events . 
  Tsarnaev will be sentenced to death or life in prison for his crimes . 
  The sentencing phase will begin the day after the 2015 race . 
  Three people died and 264 were injured in the bombing . 
 